{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In &quot;The Herd&quot;, your goal is to save as much of your herd as possible by guiding them through various hazards throughout the world</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fire:</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/extras/herdgif-fire-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738361997\" /> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Animals may not be hyper-intelligent, but they do have basic survival instincts such as avoiding fire, you can use this to your advantage to guide them!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Launch Pad:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/extras/herdgif-launch-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738361997\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is your herd being stubborn, and not moving in the direction you want on their own? Try launching them! take the control out of their hands... or hoofs.. and get them to where they need to be!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wall:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/extras/herdgif-wall-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738361997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Walls allow your to bounce and rebound your herd members,\u00a0 and must be placed strategically in order to get the most out of them!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fan:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/extras/herdgifwnd-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738361997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Sometimes your herd may need a slight nudge in the right direction, this is where the fan can be used to push them towards their goal.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fence: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Animals tend to stop running forward when there is a solid object in front of them, you can use this to funnel them into wherever you need them to go!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Dog:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/extras/herdifdog-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1738361997\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What better way to control animals then other animals! Most animals fear and will veer away from barking dogs!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Herd Mode:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*In Development</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Herd mode will feature randomly generated levels, increasing in difficulty in a roguelike fashion.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ultimate goal will be to raise the biggest herd possible, by collecting various new herd members along the way. Of course, it is possible to lose herd members along the way - so you must do everything in your power to keep them safe!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Contains 6 playable levels, allowing you to get a taste of the core gameplay.\u00a0 The full version will contain way more levels, &quot;Herd Mode&quot;, and many different kinds of animals (all with unique traits).</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738361997","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738361997","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/c7af56671242e0efeec71bf0bcc2d76e9cc5a01b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738361997","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2933210/c7af56671242e0efeec71bf0bcc2d76e9cc5a01b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738361997","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],